"parameters are shown by the little orange markers. (The upper bound of "
"the :procparam:`normalization range` is off screen in the plot above of "
"the copper foil.)"
msgstr ""
"プレエッジおよびポストエッジの線をプロットすると，:procparam:`pre-edge range` "
